rows.label: tlk42300042_02_msg0001
rows.name: Do you know of Yumyum the Burglar, mo?

rows.label: tlk42300042_02_msg0002
rows.name:
He's a Nopon phantom thief who's very popular
with children, mo!

rows.label: tlk42300042_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Apparently, he came to Invidia recently, mo.
He stole treasure from a wicked noble and
scattered it around, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300042_02_msg0004
rows.name: It seems he's already gone somewhere else, but...

rows.label: tlk42300042_02_msg0005
rows.name:
I was moved that he exists in real life,
not just in picture books, mo.
